description: List major or minor versions of a service template with detail data.

parameters.name: majorVersion
parameters.description: To view a list of minor of versions under a major version of a service template, include major Version. To view a list of major versions of a service template, exclude major Version.

parameters.name: templateName
parameters.description: The name of the service template.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates the location of the next major or minor version in the array of major or minor versions of a service template, after the current requested list of service major or minor versions.

nested_items.name: templateVersions
nested_items.description: An array of major or minor versions of a service template with detail data.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the version of a service template.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time when the version of a service template was created.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A description of the version of a service template.

nested_items.name: lastModifiedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the version of a service template was last modified.

nested_items.name: majorVersion
nested_items.description: The latest major version that's associated with the version of a service template.

nested_items.name: minorVersion
nested_items.description: The minor version of a service template.

nested_items.name: recommendedMinorVersion
nested_items.description: The recommended minor version of the service template.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The service template minor version status.

nested_items.name: statusMessage
nested_items.description: A service template minor version status message.

nested_items.name: templateName
nested_items.description: The name of the service template.
